description:
This is a 20 minute workout called '20 Minute Everyday Vinyasa Yoga Flow' from the channel Jess Yoga.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This is a 20 minute yoga flow perfect for everyday practice. Re-visit whenever you need a quick pick me up. :) 

If you enjoyed this video, be sure to give it a thumbs up and subscribe so you don't miss out on free yoga content.

See you on the mat!
